synopsis:
    sbase64.py (sbase64 [if you ran the installation script]) [-d] {input_file}
    sbase64.py (sbase64 [if you ran the installation script]) {input_file}

description:
    sbase64.py encodes or decodes a file in base64

--command
>> {PATH_TO_SARCH} {file}
abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz

--command 
>> {PATH_TO_SBASE64} -d {file}
YWJjZGVmZ2hpamtsbW5vcHFyc3R1dnd4eXoK

--output
>> YWJjZGVmZ2hpamtsbW5vcHFyc3R1dnd4eXoK

--output [-d]
>> abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz